text: Michal Šubrt (born 24 June 1967) is a Czech rower. He competed in the men's coxed four event at the 1988 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1967 births Category:Living people Category:Czech male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Czechoslovakia Category:Rowers at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Rowers from Prague
